{"tid":1261551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 於今日午後再於警總灰衫男報道中加料","createTime":"2019-06-27T09:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:30:58.000Z","uid":122379,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66d9304c717e27cf76bc3d15c1ff01e0f7d55c61","tid":1261551,"uid":122379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"凌晨開左個 POST 關於警總灰衫男報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1260200/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1260200/page/1</a><br />\n但係唔係點識 POST 相<br />\n<br />\n點知今日晏晝睇 TVB 又再加料　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzCpoFr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzCpoFr.png&h=e1c80f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbt75TP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqbt75TP.png&h=e3b3cf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGT75TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGT75TR.png&h=e9cb8db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話有人起腳踢佢<br />\n仲賴清楚咁用紅圈圈住<br />\n但係灰衫男係段片都係畀其他人遮住<br />\n點樣知道真係踢中佢？　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後灰衫男上左去佢話灰衫男係用「雪糕筒」同水刮自衛喎<br />\n但係其他報道都話係得記者跟上去<br />\n唔通灰衫男真係咁驚記者？　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前截圖﹕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWqKiQk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWqKiQk.png&h=a1e6f17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EP5aYQh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEP5aYQh.png&h=da45597e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyhs03A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpyhs03A.png&h=2ccbebb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8fsHPWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fsHPWS.png&h=556b16bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jwpveov.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwpveov.png&h=90dceb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL9nPWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL9nPWO.png&h=afb39b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成段報道就係營造到示威者對灰衫男有生命威脅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVB 我屌你老母  執柒左佢啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8c251a11772a7377e51f604cd49f416ec43de160","tid":1261551,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"你地係示威者肚條蟲?"},{"pid":"b8a6fb9629732d05c8ab070377aeeeabd814701c","tid":1261551,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"得後面冇前面<br />\nDLLM<br />\n呢個警犬想帶領衝擊仲係度幫佢講好說話"},{"pid":"1d37ec7d77b7cc3a4ee973f3baba8676b12c0ccf","tid":1261551,"uid":160605,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c251a11772a7377e51f604cd49f416ec43de160","tid":1261551,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"你地係示威者肚條蟲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"你係隻狗條蟲呀???<br />\n昨晚幾個台影撚住佢帶頭衝擊警方鐵閘....冇人跟上事敗就入返警總"},{"pid":"deeb1b95e0e208f2b21210b63a128d383901a4ce","tid":1261551,"uid":15010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"係茶記食野聽倒d食客中晒CCTVB毒<br />\nd話題全部都係咁loop段剪接片<br />\n話咩阻人返工、佢地都係打份工之類既野<br />\n<br />\n唔係撥冷水，但如果唔搞掂CCTVB，文宣好難成功<br />\n同時真係見證倒民意係幾咁容易被manipulate<br />\n明明同一班食客幾星期前都唔係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9574b25b2cbbfdaed12a26121a0ced53de7431","tid":1261551,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"想知電視城被圍的話，CCTVB會點報道